				<wikidot:authorName>stormfallen</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2782824</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The usual word used for someone who receives amnestics is &quot;amnesticized&quot;. &quot;Amnestied&quot; would refer to <a href="https://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/amnesty">amnesty</a>, which is something else entirely.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
