					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13947932#post-4850318</guid>
				<title>Author&#039;s Note</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13947932/scp-5739#post-4850318</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 21 Dec 2020 17:24:58 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Supposedly Spooky</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5529621</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>FIRST THING'S FIRST! There is a hidden message within the SCP-5739-1 instances and not everyone will find it on their first read. I'm disclosing it in the collapsable below, so consider this a warning if you'd like to go figure it out yourself.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Hidden&nbsp;Message</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Hidden&nbsp;Message</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>The first letter of every line in an SCP-XXXX-1 instance spells out a phrase.</p> </div> </div> </div> <p>Okay, other things to note.</p> <ul> <li>I drew the image and you can find more of my art <a href="https://www.instagram.com/supposedly_spooky/" target="_blank">here</a></li> <li>Please leave a comment if you've got critique!</li> </ul> <p>I think that's everything! Thank you for reading!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
